data.description: LAKE RIGHTS, CROWN POINT SCHOOLS, and a DOUBLE LOT is what this Adorable 2-STORY offers it's next owners. Yes bring your BOAT and JET SKI's the community POA access area is just down the street. Yearly POA fees and application applies. The house offers a total of 4 BEDRMS and 1.75 BATHS over 2100 SF. One bedroom is on the main level. FRENCH DOORS lead to a cozy rec room with wood burning FIREPLACE. Enjoy partial LAKE VIEWS from the back deck and FENCED in yard. There is a 1-CAR GARAGE for storage but plenty of parking available behind the garage. Take advantage of this opportunity to start enjoying lake life and schedule a showing today! Sold As-is. Showings begin 9/24/23
